<li class="toclevel-1"><a href="#Tobin_tax_projects_around_the_world"><span class="tocnumber">1</span> <span class="toctext">Tobin tax projects around the world</span></a>
<ul>
<li class="toclevel-2"><a href="#Europe"><span class="tocnumber">1.1</span> <span class="toctext">Europe</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-2"><a href="#Canada"><span class="tocnumber">1.2</span> <span class="toctext">Canada</span></a></li>
